你能够调用以下的API:
[['CrowdfundingSearch.find_projects', {'name': 'CrowdfundingSearch.find_projects', 'description': 'This function searches for crowdfunding projects based on category and status.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'category', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of the crowdfunding project, e.g., technology, art, social.'}, {'name': 'status', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The status of the project, e.g., hot, upcoming, completed.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'projects', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching projects, each with an ID, category, and status.'}]}], ['CrowdfundingSearch.get_project_details', {'name': 'CrowdfundingSearch.get_project_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific crowdfunding project given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'projectId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the crowdfunding project.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the project, including funding goal, current funding, and timeline.'}]}], ['CrowdfundingSearch.assess_project_feasibility', {'name': 'CrowdfundingSearch.assess_project_feasibility', 'description': 'This function assesses the feasibility of a crowdfunding project based on its details.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'projectId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the crowdfunding project.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'feasibility', 'description': 'An assessment of the project’s feasibility, including risks and potential returns.'}]}], ['CrowdfundingSearch.provide_participation_tips', {'name': 'CrowdfundingSearch.provide_participation_tips', 'description': 'This function provides tips for participating in a crowdfunding project based on its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'projectId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the crowdfunding project.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'tips', 'description': 'Tips for participating in the project, including how to invest and what to watch out for.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `CrowdfundingSearch.find_projects` 并传入 `category` 和 `status`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "CrowdfundingSearch.find_projects",
    "args": "{'category': 'technology', 'status': 'hot'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
